description: Campaigners say Isle of Man Bank is "letting down" elderly customers by closing two branches.
title: Protest held against IOM bank branch closures

maintext: He said he and fellow MHK Graham Cregeen, who was also at the protest, had met with the bank following its announcement, but had "not had anything more" from the company.
